WEBVTT

00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:01.016
While each of these
has had a very specific focus,

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.336
the North Star,

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:04.176
linking and guiding all of them,

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:06.640
has been Lego's powerful purpose:

00:05:07.480 --> 00:05:11.240
inspire and develop
the builders of tomorrow.

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:13.560
Expanding globally?

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:16.576
It's not about increasing sales,

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:21.240
but about giving millions of additional
children access to LEGO building bricks.

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.360
Investment and innovation?

00:05:23.960 --> 00:05:25.818
It's not about developing new products,

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:28.656
but about enabling more children

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:32.200
to experience the joy
of learning through play.